text.tspan: Age Restrictions
Untapped Market
Lack of knowledge
Time Consuming
One potential problem is the tattoo application
market is untapped. In a sense, this is an
entrepreneur’s dream, but because there are
very few tattoo related applications it is hard to
gauge the need for this type of application, and
whether or not it is scalable.
The tattoo process can be a long, daunting, and
painful. From the initial research process to
finally sitting in the chair, a lot of time has to be
committed from beginning to end to ensure one
is satisfied with their decision.
Due to the tattoo-related laws in the United
States, age restrictions will have to be
implemented to make certain that magazINK is
in compliance. This will have a major effect on
the target audience that can access the
application.
There is a huge knowledge gap when it comes to
the proper tattoo etiquette. Many people believe
getting a tattoo is as simple as finding an artist
and getting inked. Contrary to popular belief, a
lot of preparation and research is required prior
to and after getting tattooed. Majority of the
“knowledge” is obtained through word of mouth
and very opinion based which can hugely impact
someone that does not invest the time to
properly do their homework.
